  "response": "Here are several ways to make money from YouTube:\n\n1. Ad Revenue\n- Join YouTube Partner Program\n- Earn money from ads displayed on your videos\n- Requires 1,000 subscribers and 4,000 watch hours\n\n2. Sponsorships\n- Partner with brands for sponsored content\n- Promote products or services in your videos\n- Negotiate payment based on your channel's reach\n\n3. Affiliate Marketing\n- Include affiliate links in video descriptions\n- Earn commission when viewers purchase products\n- Recommend products related to your content\n\n4. Merchandise Sales\n- Create and sell branded merchandise\n- Design t-shirts, mugs, and other products\n- Use platforms like Teespring or Merch by Amazon\n\n5. Channel Memberships\n- Offer exclusive content to paying subscribers\n- Provide perks like badges and special livestreams\n- Requires 30,000 subscribers\n\n6. Super Chat and Super Stickers\n- Viewers pay to have their messages highlighted\n- Works during live streams\n- Requires monetization eligibility\n\n7. Crowdfunding\n- Use platforms like Patreon\n- Fans support your content with monthly donations\n- Offer exclusive rewards\n\n8. Online Courses/Consulting\n- Leverage your expertise\n- Sell educational content or services\n- Use YouTube to build credibility",
